groupMap - Variable in class com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.oldaccounting.OldDataBuilder
lookup map that translates account numbers to new-accounting account group; the account numbers are integers, e.g., 100.1 becomes 10010, 109.99 becomes 10999; this avoids problems with floating point representation and rounding errors for comparisons.
